result.execSummary:
The defendant Jessica L. Skilling was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Jessica L. Skilling is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Jessica L. Skilling was found guilty of Possession of Cocaine/Coca(2nd+) [Modifiers: Repeater], a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(c).
